Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.13,0:00:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:47.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1381.518,382)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.07,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁怕钳老板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(744,412)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
