Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:04.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,750)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多要好了  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost ready, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时都会好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看见没  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:14.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,788)}爱.{\fnArial}exe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不能干啥正经点的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.17,0:01:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经好几个月没客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We haven't had a customer in months
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.93,0:01:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, what is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像是个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's a
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,customer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问他要不要点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask him if he wants to order something
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.82,0:01:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉他不会点  不过我尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds unlikely, but I'll try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,280)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是真的想点餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't actually want to order anything, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有不带海霸糊的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have any food without chum?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, we do not
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来杯咖啡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just have a cup of coffee
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咖啡里面没海霸糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no chum in coffee, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没没  当然没了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no, of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给老螃蟹当间谍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spying for Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.48,0:02:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真以为我是来偷你海霸糊秘方的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to steal your secret chum formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.11,0:02:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good point
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你干嘛来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找个宁静祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I needed a nice quiet place
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又无人问津的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's completely devoid of life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.87,0:02:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来完成我的舞台剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to finish writing my stage play
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舞台剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A play, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剧情是一个才貌双全的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tells the story of a handsome and talented artist
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.84,0:02:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顽强抵抗他邪恶的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who struggles against his evil employer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.59,0:02:44.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只乖戾粗鲁的螃蟹  名叫钳老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:44.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an angry, uncouth crab named Mr. Snippers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开头写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have the beginning worked out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结尾想不出来怎么写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I just can't figure out the ending
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好也在写剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I happen to be writing a play too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,750)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲的是只暴怒大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about a big angry crab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他老是折磨一个善良无辜的店长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who torments a nice innocent shopkeeper
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我只写好了结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I only have the ending
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is destiny
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一定要一起出演咱俩的剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must put on our play, together
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我早就搭好舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I've already built a stage
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错  不过得改一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad, but we simply have to change
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这幕布的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the color of this curtain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如改成这个优美的猩红色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To this lovely shade of scarlet, for instance
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要绯红  不要猩红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It should be crimson, not scarlet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你鼻子才丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your nose is hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来你们俩得定个导演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you two need a director
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正是导演的不二之选
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm the obvious choice for director
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.63,0:04:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧  我可喜欢肆意使唤别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh please, I love bossing people around
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该让我当导演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should be the director
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来当那就肯定搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we want it ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cretin
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你们两个达不成共识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since you two can't agree on anything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就我负责导演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be the director
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, in this scene
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钳老板在痛斥他的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Snippers is berating his employees
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逼着他们划一艘古罗马战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as they row a Roman galley
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群懒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you lazy--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作  你们这群懒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to work, you lazy--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面肯定有误会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think there's been a mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我演钳老板才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am playing Mr. Snippers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钳老板这个角色正适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm perfect for the role of Mr. Snippers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知  反派戏份才最出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And everyone knows the villain is the best part
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to settle this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都得试镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll both have to audition
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试就试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I must
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will say
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正光演自己的角色我也不咋适应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not accustomed to reading for my roles anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.86,0:05:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就直接演绎经典名著集锦得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall read from a medley of classics
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罗蜊欧  罗蜊欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clameo, Clameo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:08.70,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《罗密欧与朱丽叶》\N“罗蜊欧”改回“罗密欧”即为原句 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么你偏偏是罗蜊欧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wherefore art thou, Clameo?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:15.00,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 出自《凯撒大帝》 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位罗马人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Romans
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Countrymen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你们听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lend me your ears
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1060,920)}耳朵借我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我总是指望陌生人的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have always relied on the idiocy of strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.42,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《欲望号街车》\N“愚蠢”改回“慈悲”即为原句 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来可以拥有蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could'a had Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.67,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《码头风云》\N原句为“我本来可以往上爬” ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来能偷到秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could'a had the formula
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.84,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《码头风云》\N原句为“我本来能是竞争者” ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不该只有海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instead of chum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.97,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《码头风云》\N原句为“不该是个没用的家伙” ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我现在正是这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which is all I have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.55,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 出自《码头风云》 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戏精一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a ham
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才戏精呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the one chewing the scenery
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我选好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've made my choice
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.48,0:05:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演钳老板的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The role of Mr. Snippers goes to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能让你们当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,neither of you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得选别人来演钳老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll cast someone else to play Mr. Snippers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要上哪找演员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you gonna find an actor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.62,0:05:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还要既听话  又笨到能免费干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who will follow orders
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and is dumb enough to do it for free?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去旧蛤山的公交是在这里等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this where I catch the bus to Clam Francisco?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板警告过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs did warn me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别在便宜货超市连续左转三次  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never make three left turns at the Barg'N-Mart, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钳老板的演员找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found our Mr. Snippers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你来演反派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now SpongeBob, you'll be playing the villain
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知  反派戏份才最出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows the villain is the best part
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从第56页开始演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's pick it up from page 56
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Getteth to worketh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.95,0:06:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就要碰碰你们萌萌的鼻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'm gonna giveth you a boop on your cutesy noseth
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碰碰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boop
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速去工作  不然我就打扁你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Getteth to work or I'll clobbereth thou
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你就用鼓槌打他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you hit 'em with your drumsticks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  要像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, like this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用力点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harder
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛不照着剧本去演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you following the script?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不觉得钳老板他太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Mr. Snippers is too
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演个舞台剧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a play
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剧里不念台词的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in a play, if you don't read the lines
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就等于是工作没做好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll be doing a bad job
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.53,0:07:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想把工作做好对不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to do a good job, don't you, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.07,0:07:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好好演起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now do some good acting
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快演  乖狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Act, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Act
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速去工作  不然我就打扁你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Getteth to worketh or I'll clobbereth thee
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王在上  他应该是懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By Neptune, I think he's got it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,376)}谁怕钳老板
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观剧愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the show
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说老螃蟹会过来丢人现眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think Krabs will show up for his humiliation?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给他免费送了张票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sent him a free ticket
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outta the way
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,VIP来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,VIP here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能来  我可真高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So glad you could make it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场免费舞台剧最好值回票价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This free play better be worth the money
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该遭的报应总会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll get everything that's coming to you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遭什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁怕钳老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's Afraid of Mr. Snippers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,编剧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,written by Squidward Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及谢尔顿痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And also Sheldon J. Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放第一位的应该是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should get top billing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都别想踩我谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one stands taller than Sheldon J.--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.69,0:08:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gett-eth to work-eth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.91,0:08:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可谓愚中惰者之最
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thou-est are the laziest of fools-eth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面的海报我都看到了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw that poster outside, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you like it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.10,0:09:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为呢  写第一个的应该是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For one thing it should read "Plankton and Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剧本大部分是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did most of the writing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.86,0:09:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为何不工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why-est art thou not worketh-ing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As much as I like
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看痞老板跟章鱼哥遭报应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to see Plankton and Squidward get what's coming to 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这个钳老板的人设也太恶毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think this Mr. Snippers character is a real jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当反派可真累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a villain is hard work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,职员表霸占狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Credit hog
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,江郎才尽臭写手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Washed up hack
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭写手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hack?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跑我罗马长袍里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in my toga
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wisheth
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actors
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就爱即兴发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They love improv
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,残废还是健全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To maim or not to maim
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:54.15,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《哈姆雷特》 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是个值得考虑的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is the question
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.28,0:09:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  打他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hit him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用力点打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit him harder
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop this madness
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我们别再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let us not fight
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道我们不都是海洋生物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we not all creatures of the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事实就是  你们两位的相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The truth is, you're both more alike
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多于你们的不同之处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than you are different
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.56,0:10:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我深信  你们内心深处依旧相亲相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure deep down you actually love each other
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个抢镜头的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, that little scene-stealer
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才不相亲相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We do not love each other
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们倒是有一样共识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we do agree on one thing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, get him, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打倒那个暴君钳老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that tyrant Mr. Snippers down
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能看到你们俩好好相处  我可真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy to see you two getting along
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brilliant
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是跌宕起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What an emotional roller-coaster
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想去蟹堡王一起开余兴派对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to go to the after-party at the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,余兴派对价格翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After-party prices are doubled
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你负责收银
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're running the register
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速回去工作  你个懒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get to work, you lazy bum
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钳老板说的就是这么个台词  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what Mr. Snippers would say, ain't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, good night--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:35.79,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 出自《罗密欧与朱丽叶》 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.79,标准-Chi,,800,0,0,,离别是这样甜蜜的凄清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.79,标准-Eng,,800,0,0,,Parting is such sweet sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.09,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}珊氏鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:45.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么生机勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So bustling with aquatic life
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wet
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了一只最为神出鬼没的海洋生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes one of the most elusive of sea creatures now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以帮忙给点意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you give me some feedback
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,评价我写的这份学术论文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on this scientific paper I'm writing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海洋布满了形形色色的水生生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The ocean is permeated
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a multitude of aquatic life
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从六斑玉筋鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the Ammodytes hexapterus
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再到海星纲与多孔动物门  无所不有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the Asteroidea and the Porifera
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.84,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 多孔动物门：含海绵 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生物之间虽然表面上存在着差异
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Though the differences are ostensible
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但仍有大量相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there is a plethora of similarities"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的科学论文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your science paper
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷冰冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so cold
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全是说教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so d-d-didactic
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, do you reckon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面专业内容太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's too heavy on the technical side?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉完完全全不同于
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't sound like anything
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我体验到的美妙海洋生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've experienced living in this wonderful ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既没描绘出暖流拂面的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't capture the feel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a warm current in your face
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又没捕捉到海草轻触脚趾间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or what kelp feels like between your toes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望你也能跟我一样体验海洋生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish you could experience the ocean like I do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  话说你这是想要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Sandy, what was it that you wanted to
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隆重推出  我的化鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Presenting my Fish-U-Up Machine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用这设备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this device
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把我的松鼠DNA跟鱼类DNA互换
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll swap out my squirrel DNA with fish DNA
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等换完  我就可以在水里面呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then I'll be able to breathe water
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能跟海洋生物一样亲身研究海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, I can study the ocean like y'all sea critters do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不用穿笨重的潜水服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without my bulky old suit on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢咱帅气的志愿者弗雷德大方相助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All thanks to the generous help
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of our handsome volunteer, Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.32,0:13:24.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:24.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是来这理头发的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I was getting a haircut
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按按钮吧  小方块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boop that button, square dude
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boop
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It really worked
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长鳃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have gills
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先带你出去呼吸新鲜海水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get you a breath of fresh water
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海洋很壮丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't the ocean grand?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让海水轻轻流过你的鳃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let it flow through your gills
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  相信你的鳃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, trust in your gills
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breathe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪又忘了怎么呼吸是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy forgot how to breathe, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也老是会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happens to me all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会在水里呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a water breather
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱼类的习性我还得学不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a lot I need to learn about the way of the fish
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  就比如说别吸入黄色的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like, don't breathe the yellow water
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我全身精力充沛得不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I feel more spry than a springtime pup
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要先来干什么呢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we do first, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就建议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Might I suggest
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1226,220)}港口公厕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1602,344)}鱼类内急\N解放站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,486)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.35,0:16:03.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爪子触碰青草真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:03.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this grass feels so good on my paws
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没穿潜水服  感觉蜇得更疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those stings hurt extra without my diving suit on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有点爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of invigorating
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜇我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sting me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜇我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sting me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check this out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受水母田之美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel the glory of Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,折射过来的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the refracted sunlight
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接照耀在我皮毛上的感觉真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,feels so good on my bare fur
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来深吸一口洋流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just breathe in that current
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你脱毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, you're shedding
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还长了鳞片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you've got scales
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good golly, I am and I do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的鱼类属性越来越凸显出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More of my new fish-type attributes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are making themselves known
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我还有啥鱼类特点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what other fish traits I have
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说不定我游泳技术可高超了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I got swimming skills
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个地方能确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one place to find out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻闻那四处弥漫的咸味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smell that salty waft
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还等什么呢  我的鱼类朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what are we waiting for, my fish friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.94,0:17:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海洋生物热爱水很棒吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice how sea creatures take to water, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只摸到了她的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just her pelt I felt
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.96,0:17:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你全身都是鳞片了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all scales
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好自在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel so free
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以四处灵活滑水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can glide through the water like a greased pig
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说起来  我有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, I feel hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附近的鱼类居民都吃什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do fish folk eat around these parts?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你可走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in luck
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.93,0:18:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖有全海底最棒的海滩无证小摊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goo Lagoon has the best
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unlicensed beach vendors under the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说无证  我倒想试试看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had me at "unlicensed"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.31,0:18:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份最好的鱼食小片片  大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your finest fish flakes, my good man
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dig in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这吃法还挺巧妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, ain't that clever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们吃小片片还花钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys pay for your flakes?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.21,0:18:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要吃不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I just ate
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且咱还得回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, we need to head back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变鱼真是让我大开眼界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a fish has given me all kinds of insights
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只管写你的  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just keep writing, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.72,0:18:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就带你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll get you home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么毛病  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现简直是大惊小怪得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're acting more skittish than a long-tailed cat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a roomful of rocking chairs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亮晶晶的钩子看着真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those shiny hooks look delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  离那些钩子远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, stay away from those
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可它们好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they're so
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诱人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,inviting
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.20,0:19:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要咬钩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't take the bait
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to papa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给我看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's take a look at you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自己也没好到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't no prize yourself, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附近的水里都倒了些什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are they dumping in the water around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're safe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不小心被鱼类天性冲昏头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I let my fish side get the better of me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用科学给自己改造过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You over-scienced yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得带你回实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get you back to your lab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她退化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's devolved
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta help her
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.94,0:20:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要伤害小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave Gary alone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you're safe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是等下  那珊迪是在吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, wait, then what is Sandy eating?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,布丁杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pudding cups?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你又往壳里私藏布丁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, have you been hoarding those in your shell again?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.18,0:20:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pudding
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,壳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shell
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.26,0:20:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dome
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪很有可能在树屋里藏了解药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe Sandy's hoarding antidotes back in her dome
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,布丁的事等会再算账  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll discuss this pudding thing later, young man
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,走了很多里路后
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪肯定在哪有解药
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's gotta have a remedy somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.31,0:21:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.10,0:21:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.19,0:21:41.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:41.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.86,0:21:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡浴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble bath
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪最近闻着可不大对头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy has been smelling a little fishy lately
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1190,920)}有 鱼 腥 味
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  重新进化血清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, the re-evolution serum
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进化过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too far
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你出手转危为安了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saved the day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴一切都恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad everything's back to normal
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  不过感觉好像忘了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I feel like we forgot something
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.23,0:22:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My legs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的大毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My furry, furry legs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My furry legs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.41,0:22:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.49,0:22:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.33,0:22:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿提篮来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get the carrier
